{% extends 'kegauth/multi-part-mail.j2' %}

{% block subject %}
    Password Reset Link
{% endblock %}

{% block markdown %}

Somebody asked to reset your password on {{ config.KEGAUTH_EMAIL_SITE_NAME }}.

If it **was not you**, you can safely ignore this email.

If it **was you**, click the following link to choose a new password:

<{{ kegauth.url_for('reset-password', user_id=user.id, token=user._token_plain, _external=True) }}>

{% endblock %}
